archimate:Resource.name: Dashboard
archimate:Resource.documentation: This ABB represents a set of tools that provide real-time status of the governing and governed processes and their metrics and checkpoints. It leverages the Monitoring Metric Tools ABB and Policy Enforcer ABB in the Quality of Service Layer.
